{"tid":413610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子中環街頭搶警槍失手　遭兩警制服","createTime":"2017-09-25T14:18:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T16:26:14.000Z","uid":20933,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81e1cc95534cf93142b6549537314aa081c0cec5","tid":413610,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170925/large/1506348299_b8cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170925%2Flarge%2F1506348299_b8cd.jpg&h=00cd473e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中環晚上發生搶警槍案！兩名軍裝警員晚上近9時巡邏期間，當巡經皇后大道中329號對開時，突然一名年約30至40歲男子迎面而來，一聲不響強搶其中一名警員的手槍，兩警奮力抵抗，最終將搶槍男制服拘捕。據知，疑犯已被帶署調查，警方仍了解其犯案動機。"},{"pid":"b8e37ccd5894dccdc20b488e400b30eb7ab911c6","tid":413610,"uid":36178,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:21:41.000Z","msg":"邊有可能就咁搶到槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a5b7ec04660ec5b91a4f6805d74dcc44d7077c3","tid":413610,"uid":118120,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:25:55.000Z","msg":"玩命"},{"pid":"206c8e82b3c00828f1c6e22b27f493b71faea7eb","tid":413610,"uid":7355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:30:38.000Z","msg":"係咪飲醉"},{"pid":"5ae146209d99a90f0ef3e5764fa26a330137e589","tid":413610,"uid":26451,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:31:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"17f51c8c21d4c54f3bd98f1532636557b883495e","tid":413610,"uid":1900,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:35:26.000Z","msg":"槍袋有特別設計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔識既話冇咩可以搶到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c716d5b517289a8b831a85780c62be4e43b14a62","tid":413610,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-2