0f1e539","tid":413610,"uid":56878,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T15:33:56.000Z","msg":"係唔係罪公安比人屈"},{"pid":"0bb11161ca680f759fa680fed6778b0ec0670011","tid":413610,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T15:34:30.000Z","msg":"反槍狗又話搶槍好易，槍唔可以自衛既？"},{"pid":"4266e842e8a6ee06e9ed8a5bae6833830c1ead7f","tid":413610,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T23:53:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"411d246ed7137ad2ed9441c80becabd089c703ed","tid":413610,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T23:55:56.000Z","msg":"搏拉 又同你講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573b91e7f2000c8b3045065baa517ee55c8d64b7","tid":413610,"uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T00:02:23.000Z","msg":"現時軍裝警員所用的M-10佩槍，長22.5厘米，可載六發子彈，並無保險掣;美國製直拔式槍袋，槍柄外露，槍袋頂部安裝鈕扣活動皮扣，袋內亦有鋼夾夾實，保護發射掣固定設計，警員拔槍時需先握槍柄，用拇指逼開頂部活動皮扣鈕扣，再將槍推前以壓緊槍身令鐵片鬆開，才能拔出佩槍。<br />\n<br />\n警方內部有向警員進行防搶槍訓練，有資深警官指，警員在學堂已有學防搶槍技巧，在職者每三個月的「季燒（燒槍）」訓練，亦要重溫有關技巧，無論被人從前後左右搶槍，首要是用手緊按防搶鈕扣，另一隻手按實佩槍或搶槍者的手，身軀下墜讓搶槍者「撲空」，再向無槍方向轉身，與疑人保持距離。"},{"pid":"26bc19b0fa48164655c2b2757d9c56d70cd1ee18","tid":413610,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T00:05:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf92ce179b227c2e52f537632fcb23eb9d29d8f","tid":413610,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T00:25:36.000Z","msg":"估下咩國籍"},{"pid":"78831473a5b211d7248be370c6e11b4d8f9e71b1","tid":413610,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T00:46:16.000Z","msg":"蝻"},{"pid":"6ea0685eb5561d0096c804982403fb2c66c39624","tid":413610,"uid":10650,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:17:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>槍袋有特別設計<img src=\"/ass